props.name: Love is in the Air
props.description: Valentine's day is here and boxes of chocolates are flying of the shelf!

props.name: Galactic Outreach
props.description: An emerging civilization needs to fight a health epidemic but is not ready for more advanced eggs. We need your help!

props.name: Hangover Cure
props.description: It's the day after St. Patrick's day and folks had a little too much to drink, hangover cures are out of stock!

props.name: Spring Cleaning
props.description: Spring Cleaning is starting early due to the wild popularity of Marie Kondo's new book. Quantum storage is in high demand!

props.name: Space Vacation
props.description: Space Tourism is way up this year and there are rocket fuel shortages everywhere!

props.name: Teslegg Model F
props.description: After a long wait Teslegg has released their mass market fusion powered car! Fusion eggs are in high demand.

props.name: Diapers Everywhere!
props.description: The creator of Egg, Inc. (me) just had a baby!  I need y'all to work together to make me some quantum waste pails to help with all the diapers!

props.name: Operation: Habitapull
props.description: A science project aims to move a planet into the habitable zone of a nearby star system. Graviton egg demand is spiking.

props.name: Spring is Here
props.description: What a beautiful day isn't it? No better way to start off the day than with 2 fried eggs, at it appears everyone agrees.

props.name: April Fool
props.description: A tech company's April Fools jokes went too far causing trillions in damages. Let's go back in time and stop the bad jokes!

props.name: Easter Egg Shortage
props.description: With so many planned easter eggs hunts around the galaxy, there is a shortage. We need your help!

props.name: Tax Headache
props.description: It's time to file taxes! Headache cures are in high demand. Help fill the orders!

props.name: Cinco de Oh-no
props.description: Cinco de Mayo celebrators partied a little too hard and have depleted pain killer supplies, time to restock!

props.name: Housing Boom!
props.description: There are housing shortages all over the galaxy, the building boom needs more Super Material eggs to catch up!

props.name: Mother's Day Begins
props.description: Chocolate makers are trying to get a jump on Mother's day this year. Help them out with this endurance contract.

props.name: Back to the Moon
props.description: With renewed plans to colonize the moon, rocket fuel is in high demand. Let us boldly go!

props.name: CleanX
props.description: To make room for more satellites, we need to clean up space! Over 500,000 pieces of space trash need to be pulled back to earth. So we're building a Graviton Canon!

props.name: The New Mac Pro!
props.description: Apple has placed an huge order of Super Material eggs for the crazy new Mac Pro case!

props.name: School's Out!
props.description: A new batch of students have earned their certification to consume Prodigy Eggs!

props.name: Waterballoon Fight!
props.description: The longest day of the year is here (norther hemisphere) and you know what that means!

props.name: Heat Waves
props.description: Heat waves are being reported all over the planet, help everyone cool off!

props.name: LEGO Tower!
props.description: Everyone is building LEGO towers. Super Material eggs are needed to form all the bricks! (download LEGO Tower today!)

props.name: Stockpile Fireworks
props.description: Early orders indicate this is going to be a big 4th of July in the states! Time to start stockpiling fireworks!

props.name: Federal Reggserve
props.description: With so many piggy breaks during Eggcelebration, the Federal Reggserve is all out of Golden Eggs! The Mint needs Super Material eggs to forge more!

props.name: Edible Shortage
props.description: With the discovery of new Boosts, farmers are quickly moving to pricier eggs leading to a scarcity of Edible Eggs, we need your help!

props.name: Summer Activities
props.description: Summer activities are at an all time high, and that means so are injuries! Help meet the demand for Medical eggs.

props.name: Summer Heat
props.description: With summer heat in full swing, AC is running non stop and some power plants need more fuel!

props.name: Moon Vacation
props.description: Folks are squeezing in their final summer trips and the Moon is this years most popular destination, more fuel is needed!

props.name: Back To School
props.description: Back-to-school students are in need of a refresher, Teachers need tachyon eggs to send kinds back in time to review material they forgot over summer.

props.name: 3D Printing
props.description: 3D printing is blowing up and there are filament shortages all over, Super Material eggs are needed!

props.name: Help The Amazon
props.description: The Amazon Rainforest continues to burn at unprecedented levels, waterballoon eggs are needed! Auxbrain, Inc has donated to the Rainforest Alliance to help.

props.name: Superfood Mystery
props.description: A mysterious company is buying incredible amounts of Superfood Eggs, can you meet the demands?

props.name: Air Conditioning
props.description: With heat waves sweeping the southwest, Air Conditioners are running non stop, more fuel is needed for Fusion reactors!

props.name: Kissing Chickens
props.description: The CDC warns chicken lovers to stop kissing chickens due to a salmonella outbreak (Seriously, Google It)! Medical Eggs are needed!

props.name: Pumpkin Time!
props.description: It is officially Fall (in the northern hemisphere), you know what that means! Pumpkin all the things!

props.name: Starship EG1
props.description: Space Eggs is testing a new MASSIVE rocket and it needs a lot of fuel for all the test launches!

props.name: Rooftop Solar
props.description: While advanced eggs have made energy clean, Rooftop solar panels are still saving people money! Help meet demand for raw materials!

props.name: Fire Season
props.description: It's fire season in California, fire departments are putting in large orders of Water-balloon eggs to prepare.

props.name: Pumpkin Prep
props.description: Halloween looking to be big this year, Pumpkins are sold out and more are needed

props.name: Sci-Fire
props.description: A new startup need your help to produce Graviton eggs for their latest fire fighting drones!

props.name: Tummy Aches
props.description: Kids are eating too much candy after Halloween and it's causing shortages of stomach medication!

props.name: A Trip Back
props.description: People are honoring the sacrifices of those who serve by taking a trip back in time. Help them on their journey.

props.name: CyberSteel
props.description: Despite controversial styling the new Truck from Teslegg has become a must have for Egg Farmers. More raw materials are needed!

props.name: Ten for Ten
props.description: It's a busy time of year for bakers, orders for Edible eggs have quadrupled!

props.name: More Pumpkins?!
props.description: We thought we hand enough for Thanksgiving, we were wrong. Rush order!

props.name: Pumpkin Pie
props.description: It's that time of year, when what is widely considered the greatest pie hits center stage: Pumpkin Pie.

props.name: Stuffed
props.description: Folks have been over-eating for days and are looking for lighter meals, Superfood eggs are flying off the shelves

props.name: Three Amigos
props.description: The county fair is holding a content for teams of 3 farmers to win big prizes!

props.name: Holiday Lights
props.description: With homes and businesses firing up their Holiday lights and decorations, local power generation needs more juice!

props.name: Last Minute Shipping
props.description: Shipping companies are slammed! More Quantum storage is needed!

props.name: Hangover Cure
props.description: The big new years parties are scheduled, partiers are planning ahead this year and buying hangover cures before hand!

props.name: Help Australia
props.description: Fires in Australia have reached historic size and devastation, Waterballoon eggs are needed! Auxbrain, Inc. has donated to the Australian Red Cross to help.

props.name: I Have a Dream
props.description: As recent the battle for civil rights may be, we none the less must look back to understand our present.

props.name: Folding Screens
props.description: While it is unclear who wants a folding screen, at this year's Consumer Electronics Show they were all the rage! Raw materials are needed!

props.name: LEO Internet
props.description: Satellite Constellation Internet is all the rage in commercial space flight! Help fuel the launches!

props.name: Outbreak
props.description: The word races to contain and support the outbreak of a new virus. Get the facts from your local government health agency (eg. cdc.gov)

props.name: Love is in the Egg
props.description: Valentine's Day is right around the corner and chocolate makers are working overtime to meet orders!

props.name: Something Out There
props.description: The discovery of the remains of an ancient civilization in a distant solar system has caused a resurgence of deep space exploration!

props.name: Leap Year Festival
props.description: Leap Year Festivals around the world need Tachyon eggs for various rituals!

props.name: Restoration
props.description: Recently returned interplanetary artifacts posses mysterious properties, archeologists are trying to restore them to see what power they might possess

props.name: Good Ol' Fusion
props.description: A new orbital outpost needs fuel! It's a good o' fashion fusion supply contract!

props.name: Quantitative Egging
props.description: The economy is taking a hit and the government is buying up loads of eggs to keep everyone afloat!

props.name: Quarantine
props.description: While billions are in self quarantine, orders of Superfood eggs for home meals have exploded! Stay safe at home. Auxbrain has donated $500 to a food service worker support fund.

props.name: Shop at Home
props.description: With the incredible surge of at home delivery for just about everything Quantum storage solutions are booming!

props.name: Egg Pre Orders
props.description: Easter is around the corner, so naturally store are starting to stock up!

props.name: Chocolate Refill
props.description: The shelves of chocolate are empty at grocery stores, help fill the new orders!

props.name: Arts and Crafts
props.description: Kids are completing more arts and crafts projects than ever, we need more supplies!

props.name: LEGACY: Laurel vs Yanny
props.description: A Quantum rift is causing people to hear different words in a viral video. Scientists have a fix but they need your help.

props.name: Snack Attack
props.description: For an unknown reason baked goods are flying off the shelves and more eggs are needed to restock!

props.name: Megg The 4th Be With You
props.description: Levitation products and tricks are being cleared out of stores, suppliers need to refill orders!

props.name: LEGACY: Home Renovations
props.description: You've decided to build a new house! Why not make it yourself? You'll need a lot of eggs so get started!

props.name: Personal Mobility
props.description: The UnoWheel EggR personal mobility device was just released. Powered by Fusion Eggs, it has over 100 miles of range! Eggs are needed!

props.name: LEGACY: All or Nothing
props.description: A mysterious investor is looking for a lot of edible eggs. But he wants the full amount or nothing.

props.name: Supermarket Refill
props.description: With so many restaurants closed, supermarkets weren't ready for Edible Egg demand for Mother's day omelettes!

props.name: Tachy-gone
props.description: "Time tourism" broke all records this memorial day depleting tachyon egg inventories, time to help stock back up!

props.name: LEGACY: SpaceEggs
props.description: Spaceflight is booming due to re-usable rockets. Help fill the demand with this contract.

props.name: LEGACY: Anxiety Attack
props.description: A new school year and political turmoil have everyone stressed out! A regimen of medical eggs are needed.

props.name: Chocolate Rush
props.description: For an unknown reason chocolate won't stay on the shelves, help meet the high demand!

props.name: Shipping Surge
props.description: A surge in bulk shipping has created an opportunity for quantum egg farmers, join in on the rush!

props.name: LEGACY: New Civilization
props.description: A group of explorers are setting out to find new worlds, new civilizations. They are in need of fuel!

props.name: Summer Solstice
props.description: With summer solstice around the corner, the Global Egg Festival is about to kick off. Edible eggs are needed!

props.name: LEGACY: Tool Time!
props.description: It's father's day around the galaxy and power tools are flying off the shelves. Help restock!

props.name: New Formula
props.description: The genetic formula has been tweaked this year leading to record demand for firework eggs this year!

props.name: LEGACY: Ouch!
props.description: With all those new power tools out there, there are lots of minor injuries. First Aid!

props.name: Heating Up
props.description: Summer is heating up and you know what that means.... Waterballoon fight!

props.name: LEGGACY: Last Minute
props.description: More fireworks are needed ASAP!

props.name: Hot Fireworks
props.description: With a surge in at-home fireworks shows, burn treatments are flying off the shelves, help restock!

props.name: LEGGACY: Time Tourism
props.description: (From Memorial Day 2018) so called "Time Tourism" is booming and Tachyon eggs are in short supply!

props.name: E-Day
props.description: Egg Day is once again upon us (July 14), and everyone is looking for the classic.

props.name: LEGGACY: Egg Day 2018
props.description: Some folks like to celebrate Egg Day with a bang!

props.name: Summer Fitness
props.description: August is the most popular month to vacation, people are dieting to get their bodies ready for the beach!

props.name: LEGGACY: Engage!
props.description: (2018) The Federation of planets needs more fuel for their star fleet!

props.name: Secret Projects
props.description: Space Agencies around the globe are expanding deep space exploration, Rocket Fuel is in short supply!

props.name: LEGGACY: Summer Sunset
props.description: The local town has commissioned you to create the waterballoons for the end of summer waterballoon fight! (2018)

props.name: Video Games
props.description: With folks playing more PC and Console games than ever before, home energy needs are up!

props.name: LEGGACY: Just Chocolate
props.description: Sometimes chocolate demand spikes, and all we gotta do as egg farmers is make more chocolate. (2018)

props.name: Ion Drive
props.description: Aerospace companies need Fusion eggs for an experimental Ion Thruster project.

props.name: LEGGACY: Nostalgia
props.description: July 14 (2018) is Egg Day around the galaxy and everyone like to celebrate with the egg that started it all...

props.name: Cool Off
props.description: As heat waves take over the country, waterballoons are in short supply!

props.name: Orbital Fueling
props.description: A new orbital fueling rig has begun operation, it needs copious amounts of Quantum Eggs!

props.name: LEGGACY: Getting Ready
props.description: With 4th of July (2018) nearing in the States, scientists have found a new way to meet the demand for fireworks...

props.name: LEGGACY: A Clever Solution
props.description: As drought wreaks havoc on agriculture, farmers are looking for water in unusual places... (2018)

props.name: LEGGACY: Mother's Day Brunch
props.description: Mothers all over the galaxy are requesting omelettes and french toast for breakfast! (2018)

props.name: Bluetooth Pigs
props.description: Bluetooth enabled pigs are the new hot pet! Neuro-implant makers need more materials!

props.name: Space Food
props.description: A biomedical firm is developing food for space travelers based heavily on superfood eggs.

props.name: LEGGACY: Complex Costumes
props.description: Halloween (2018) costume manufacturing has started. These are sophisticated scary costumes that need some high tech components.

props.name: Made In Space
props.description: A space exploration firm is building a spaceship factory.. in space!

props.name: LEGGACY: Chocolate!
props.description: Didn't take scientists long to figure out the smart thing to do was to just make chickens lay chocolate eggs. (2018)

props.name: Hydrogen Dreams
props.description: After a hydrogen fuel cell car company was revealed to be a fraud, Teslegg Fusion car sales are surging!

props.name: Color Change
props.description: As the leaves change color so do the eggs. Help meet seasonal demand!

props.name: LEGGACY: Super Food Drive
props.description: (2018) Egg Farmers have flocked to high value eggs leaving people hungry! We need some Superfood eggs stat!

props.name: LEGGACY: Fall Festival Competition
props.description: The (2018) Fall Festival egg laying competition is here!

props.name: Fall Flu
props.description: Flu season is getting started, and folks are stocking up preventative medications!

props.name: LEGGACY: Pumpkin Crunch
props.description: (2018) Pumpkins are in super high demand... leave it to the chickens to deliver the goods!

props.name: Tricker Treats
props.description: Time to help make everyone's favorite Halloween treat!

props.name: LEGGACY: A New Sun
props.description: (2018) A new solar system has been found with multiple habitable planets in need of terraforming!

props.name: Quantum Ballot Box
props.description: The new Quantum Ballot boxes can securely store millions of ballots. Make sure you (or your parents) are planning to vote!

props.name: LEGGACY: Moon Food
props.description: (2019) Moon colony food stores were tainted without government food inspectors to check for contaminants. Help send some food!

props.name: Last Minute Decoration
props.description: Family meetings were called, one common conclusion: We need more pumpkins!

props.name: LEGGACY: Halloween Blitz
props.description: (2018) Pumpkin demand is overwhelming! A quick contract for big money!

props.name: Prototypes
props.description: SpaceEggs is prototyping giant rockets at an incredible pace. Supplies are needed!

props.name: LEGGACY: Moon Rockets
props.description: Moon colony food stores were tainted. The food is ready on earth, just need more fuel! (2019)

props.name: Tachyon Deflector
props.description: Researchers are developing a device to prevent the adverse effects of deep space travel on the human body.

props.name: More Pie
props.description: Even with holiday travel at all time lows, the demand for pumpkin pie has never been higher!

props.name: LEGGACY: Wildfires
props.description: (2018) Climate change is wreaking havoc on dryer climates. Wildfires are rampant but now there is a way egg farmers can help! (Egg, Inc. has donated $500 to the American Red Cross)

props.name: Small Reactors
props.description: The popularity of new compact dilithium reactors are spiking demand for the fuel!

props.name: LEGGACY: Fusion Tankers
props.description: The world's largest ocean shipping company is putting ultra compact fusion reactors in all their tankers. Long term work available.(2018)

props.name: Leftovers
props.description: (2018) Thanksgiving has left the world with too many leftovers, quantum Tupperware is sold out everywhere, and more raw materials are needed.

props.name: Quantum Monday
props.description: With nearly all Holiday shopping happening online, Quantum storage solutions are in high demand!

props.name: LEGGACY: World Record Egg
props.description: (2019) With a simple picture of an Egg becoming the most liked social media post, demand for the classic is booming!

props.name: Toy Builders
props.description: Toy sales are off the charts this year with manufacturers scrambling to buy raw materials!

props.name: Winter Break
props.description: (2018) It's Winter Break! And since break homework was deemed cruel and unusual punishment, Prodigy Eggs are all the rage!

props.name: Holidegg
props.description: Tasty holiday food and drink such as Egg Nog and Noodle Kugel are spiking demand for regular eggs!

props.name: LEGGACY: The Thaw
props.description: (2019) Half the USA is frozen over from an Arctic Blast! Fusion egg reserves are depleted for home heaters and de-icers.

props.name: Space Food 2.0
props.description: Engineered foods based on Superfood eggs are in mass production for deep space travel. Ingredients needed!

props.name: Space Bots
props.description: New tiny space robots have been developed to explore space, small enough to be launched with traditional fuels!

props.name: LEGGACY: Resolutions
props.description: It's that time of year, everyone is headed to the gym and getting on a strict diet of Superfood Eggs!

props.name: 2020 Hangover
props.description: Is it possible to have a hangover from a year? Doctors are prescribing medical eggs to patients with mysterious headaches and nausea.

props.name: LEGGACY: Quantum Trash Bags
props.description: (2018) With all the wrapping paper and boxes to throw out, Quantum Trash bags are flying off the shelves!

props.name: Ion Drive II
props.description: The once experimental high thrust ion drive is now ready for test flights. Fusion eggs needed!

props.name: LEGGACY: History Lesson
props.description: (2019) In appreciation of Martin Luther King day people around the world take a trip back to witness first hand key moments in world history!

props.name: Lost Civilizations
props.description: The boom in deeps space travel has led to the discovery of strange items. Scientists need materials to prototype containers to harness their unusual energy signature.
